**Troubleshooting**

- If you see path-length or CMake errors on Windows, create a short junction to the project root and build from there (example used during development):

```powershell
cmd /c mklink /J "C:\numtowords" "G:\Code_Playground\Android Developement\NumToWords"
Set-Location -LiteralPath 'C:\numtowords\android'
.\gradlew.bat assembleRelease
```

- If Kotlin/CMake incremental cache errors occur, try stopping Gradle daemon and cleaning build caches:

```powershell
.\gradlew.bat --stop
.\gradlew.bat clean
```

